casebody.data:
In re Resignation of Bray.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Bray (1990), 53 Ohio St. 3d 601.]

(No. 90-1138 Submitted July 19, 1990 Decided July 25, 1990.)

The resignation of Edward J. Bray as an attorney is accepted.

Moyer, C. J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
